description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10MIN full body pilates workout // de-bloating & flexibility // beginner friendly' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: a perfect 10-minute full body movement for increased mobility, flexibility that will make you feel happy and relaxed, perfect for early mornings or some relaxing evening movement! 

Hope you have fun doing this workout! 
Love you all, Lidi x
